descript.abstract: Selected housing and population indicators derived from the "2010 Census Summary File 1" published by the U.S. Census Bureau, summarized on a census block basis. All indicators have numerators and denominators except in cases of total population counts and averages. Numerators are denoted with "_N" and Denominators with "_D".
descript.purpose: Demographic analysis and visualization. Users are strongly advised to thoroughly read this metadata record and 2010 Summary File 1 documentation available from the U.S. Census Bureau at http://www.census.gov/prod/cen2010/doc/sf1.pdf. A copy of this technical documentation is included with the data download file available from RIGIS.
descript.supplinf: The primary data source, "2010 Census Summary File 1" published by the U.S. Census Bureau, may be accessed online via American Fact Finder (http://factfinder2.census.gov) or directly via http://www2.census.gov/census_2010/04-Summary_File_1/Rhode_Island. The original TIGER/Line shapefile that serves as the spatial reference for these data may be downloaded from http://www.census.gov/geo/www/tiger/tgrshp2010/tgrshp2010.html.

procstep.procdesc: Downloaded 2010 Summary File 1 tabular data and census block spatial data from the U.S. Census Bureau. Reprojected census block data to Rhode Island State Plane coordinate system. Extracted selected indicators from Summary File 1 database, joined to census block spatial data, created, named, and calculated appropriate fields as necessary. Please note that each demographic attribute description contains information about which SF1 tables were used to calculate each individual field.

Data contributed to RIGIS by The Providence Plan. Metadata written. Please note that those original attribute definitions sourced from the original U.S. Census Bureau metadata record for the source 2010 Census Block boundaries have been duly credited.
